    "text": "Consumer Protection Relief Fund Act or the CPR Fund Act \n\nThis bill establishes the Consumer Protection Relief Fund for vulnerable borrowers experiencing financial difficulty in repaying specified loans due to the impact of COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019). Aggregate payments with respect to a borrower may not exceed $9,500."
